  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The reason was that three-- he had three officers, one second lieutenant and two first lieutenants, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of which two out of three we helped in Lyons.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And because he didn't like them, they told him that I did so much for them in Lyons, staying in the Hotel Perrache.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And one of them by the name of Sondberchen was a little-- a bit of a schlemazel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I got him out via [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE] three times of prison from [INAUDIBLE] on the [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Sea. ?] He felt that I'm a bad boy because he didn't like these, his officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by not liking me, he appointed me and another guy-- not Barend Boers-- that we should be the first to go-- we were only talking about Africa.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not talking about Europe-- being what we called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means you-- if you have a brigade, we need some people to go first to make space for the infantry, the artillery, you know, for the brigade, you know, whatever they have got.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the 20-- connected with the artillery, which were the 25-pounders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had eight of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they appointed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they, they, they told me that I'm the OP post.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OP post stands for Observation Post, which goes in front of the infantry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they usually pick a site which is a bit high, which could be a church, which could be a mountain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you direct the 25-pounders, which was the heavy artillery, towards a certain project or subject.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you had this, you only use one of the 25-pounders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you find the right [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] project, the right position, then all the other ones can start shooting.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
